cs.HC, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.CYBER, cs.NI 

This paper discusses the development of a Virtual Rehabilitation Environment (VRE) using different web systems and technologies. The focus is on the performance and scalability of the system, which falls under the categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), databases (cs.DB), software engineering (cs.SE), cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
